name: Helios
description: Helios is a rocky, barren world scorched by the intense radiation of its nearby star.

name: Aurelia
description: Aurelia is a desert planet characterized by vast sandy dunes and rocky plateaus.

name: Veridia Prime
description: Veridia Prime is a lush, vibrant world teeming with diverse ecosystems and abundant life.

name: Vulcan
description: Vulcan is a volcanic world, with its surface marred by towering volcanoes, lava flows, and geysers of molten rock.

name: Aurora
description: Aurora is a rocky planet with a striking appearance, featuring vast canyons, towering mountains, and glowing auroras that dance across its sky.

name: Cerulea
description: Cerulea is a water-dominated world, with its surface mostly covered by vast, deep oceans.

name: Eclipta
description: Eclipta is an icy world, perpetually shrouded in a thick layer of frost and snow.

name: Aether
description: Aether is a mysterious planet shrouded in swirling mists and dense clouds.

name: Zephyr
description: Zephyr is a gas giant with swirling bands of colorful clouds and a turbulent atmosphere.
